message: Hello Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product which is valued at $15000 to you. Considering its exceptional quality and the benefits it offers, I am proposing to sell it to you for $12000. This price not only reflects its true value but also provides you with a significant saving compared to the market rate. I believe this offer presents an excellent opportunity for both of us. Please let me know if you are interested in proceeding with this offer.
